import { FaUserCircle } from 'react-icons/fa'; import '../stylesheets/Profile.css'; import Back from './BackButton'; import Logout from './LogoutButton'; import Settings from './SettingsButton' function ProfilePage() { const data = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('userData')) return(
< FaUserCircle className ="user-icon"/>

{data.nameFirst} {data.nameLast}

@{data.email}

Address: {data.address}

Phone Number: {data.phone}

Rides Given: {data.ridesGiven}

Rides Taken: {data.ridesTaken}

) } export default ProfilePage
